{"tid":1616712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 今晚22:00 有民間記者會！","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:48:15.000Z","uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5e3233f3c3f22fbed9c1050ce0a1eb4b456d18","tid":1616712,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會緊急採訪通知<br />\n<br />\n今日有多間傳媒報導，政府將以緊急法訂立反蒙面法，民間記者會會作出回應，表示市民毋懼惡法，誓死頑抗，歡迎政府視香港經濟及國際地位為無物，齊齊攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年10月3日（星期四）<br />\n時間：晚上10:00<br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019 年 10月3日"},{"pid":"1034b1f42d971ec15bac723a3f8ff807cd0b114f","tid":1616712,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a471884f5c01bbcc769d22f87102349100d8a593","tid":1616712,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1616373/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1616373/page/1</a> 我屌你地同我入去填同幫我推"}]}